title: Orange is the New Bat
description:
Mindy and Guy Raz are heading to a bat convention, but why did Mindy make a bright orange bat costume for Guy Raz?! It's time to meet the newly discovered species, MYOTIS NIMBAENSIS! It's the who, what, when, where, why, how and WOW of BATS SPECIES!
